<h1 class="logoline">Get Together with <%= image_tag( 'logo.svg', alt: 'GatherPack', class: 'logo') %> GatherPack</h1>

<p class="lead mb-4 text-center">People Management | Time &amp; Attendance Tracking | Event Planning | Money Management</p>

<%= partial :beta_cta %>

<div class="card bg-body-secondary text-white mx-1 mx-md-5 mt-5">
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="fs-3 fw-light text-center lh-sm">
      GatherPack was created by a FIRST mentor &amp; team members to support FIRST programs.
      GatherPack helps manage your students, mentors, parents, alumni, and your whole community in one place. 
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mx-md-5">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Organization</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-3 col-xl-1 text-end">
        <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-chart-diagram"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-9 col-xl-11">
        <p class="fs-5">Make GatherPack your single source of truth for who's who and what's what.</p>
        <ul class="fa-ul">
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i></span>Organize your people into teams</li>
          <ul class="fa-ul">
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-diagram-project"></i></span>Create sub-teams (and sub-sub-teams)</li>
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i></span>Assign managers to teams that can manage content, events, and people on their teams</li>
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pyramid"></i></span>And, coming soon, create titles &amp; org charts for your teams, events, and your entire organization.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-seal"></i></span>Grant people badges to track accomplishments and achievements</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mx-md-5">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Communication</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-3 col-xl-1 text-end">
        <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-messages"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-9 col-xl-11">
        <p class="fs-5">GatherPack helps keep your team members, parents, and mentors connected and informed.</p>
        <ul class="fa-ul">
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-message-captions"></i></span>Post scheduled announcements for individual teams or for everyone in your organization</li>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-mailbox-flag-up"></i></span>Send out regularly scheduled personalized announcement &amp; activity summaries via email</li>
          <ul class="fa-ul">
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-bell"></i></span>Or, send notifications immediately when publishing a new announcement</li>
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i></span>And coming soon, send notifications via text, mobile push notification, Discord, Slack, etc.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-info"></i></span>Create content pages to share important information and resources</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mx-md-5">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Events</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-3 col-xl-1 text-end">
        <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-calendars"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-9 col-xl-11">
        <p class="fs-5">Let GatherPack track events, activities, and important dates for your team.</p>
        <ul class="fa-ul">
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-lines-pen"></i></span>Post events to your team's calendar</li>
          <ul class="fa-ul">
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-users"></i></span>Track who's coming - and who's not - to each event.</li>
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-field"></i></span>Assign custom fields to event types to track hotel room assignments, transportation methods, and whatever else you need to know.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-cake-candles"></i></span>Keep track of all your team members' birthdays</li>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i></span>And, coming soon, display your GatherPack calendar with your Google Calendar or other calendar tools.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mx-md-5">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Time Tracking</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-3 col-xl-1 text-end">
        <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-9 col-xl-11">
        <p class="fs-5">GatherPack tracks meeting &amp; volunteer hours.</p>
        <ul class="fa-ul">
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-timer"></i></span>Create time clock periods to track and report on different activities.</li>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-clock"></i></span>Manually input time clock entries, or use the time clock kiosk to get people to track their own time.</li>
          <ul class="fa-ul">
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-nfc"></i></span>Use PIN numbers, a barcode scanner, an RFID reader, or other methods to let people clock in &amp; out at the kiosk.</li>
          </ul>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mx-md-5">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Finances</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-3 col-xl-1 text-end">
        <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-money-bill-trend-up"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-9 col-xl-11">
        <p class="fs-5">Keep an eye on your team's finances with GatherPack.</p>
        <ul class="fa-ul">
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-receipt"></i></span>Handle your organization's books with our simple financial ledger system.</li>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments-dollar"></i></span>Add tags to transactions for better organization and tracking.</li>
          <ul class="fa-ul">
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-piggy-bank"></i></span>And, coming soon, automatically pull transactions into GatherPack from your bank account.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-money-check-pen"></i></span>Accept online payments &amp; donations.</li>
          <ul class="fa-ul">
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-brands fa-cc-stripe"></i></span>Accept credit cards, bank transfer, and dozens of other payment methods via Stripe.</li>
            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fa-brands fa-cc-paypal"></i></span>And, coming soon, PayPal &amp; Venmo support.</li>
          </ul>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card bg-body-secondary text-white mx-1 mx-md-5">
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="fs-3 fw-light text-center lh-sm">
      Host GatherPack yourself, or let us deal with that for you - with a significantly discounted hosting fee* for FIRST teams.
    </p>

    <p class="small text-center fw-light mx-5">
      * We're still working out pricing for our hosting service as we're doing our beta test roll-out.
      We intend to do hosting for FIRST teams "at cost" - which is looking like about $20/month.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

